               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿmāda mǝśṭir "The Five Pillars of Mystery’’ (fols.
                     5r-83r)&#xD; I-1) Introduction (fols. 5ra-9vb)&#xD; I-2) Mǝśṭira Śǝllāse
                     “Mystery of the Trinity” (fols. 10ra-21rb)&#xD; I-3) Mǝśṭira śǝggāwe “Mystery
                     of the Incarnation” (fols. 21va-55v)&#xD; I-4) Mǝśṭira ṭǝmqat “Mystery of
                     Baptism” (fols. 55v-65r)&#xD; I-5) Mǝśṭira qʷǝrbān “Mystery of the Eucharist”
                     (fols. 65r-77ra)&#xD; I-6) Mǝśṭira tǝnśāʾe mutān “Mystery of the Resurrection
                     of the Dead” (fols. 77ra-83r)&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
